channel.title: Problem with logging in (i'm owner everybody else is on)
channel.description:
[b]PLEASE READ THE WHOLE THING TO UNDERSTAND MY PROBLEM[/b]
I'm the owner, I was on earlier but now I can't log in. It seems to be after I started up the wrong source then when I ran the new source it stopped working. I log in and when the screen says loading please wait it just stays like that forever. Plus I can load java things with the server up ~ which I couldn't do before this problem. If anybody has any idea what the problem is please tell me. Or if you can think of anything that I could try to fix the problem. Everybody else is logged in but me :( Please help.
